<li id="cite_note-FirstDrafts-6"><b><a href="#cite_ref-FirstDrafts_6-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFRobert_McCrum2004">Robert McCrum (2004-01-18). <a href="http://books.guardian.co.uk/news/articles/0,6109,1125534,00.html" class="external text" title="http://books.guardian.co.uk/news/articles/0,6109,1125534,00.html" rel="nofollow">"First drafts"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Guardian_Unlimited" title="Guardian Unlimited" class="mw-redirect">Guardian Unlimited</a></i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.guardian.co.uk/news/articles/0,6109,1125534,00.html" class="external free" title="http://books.guardian.co.uk/news/articles/0,6109,1125534,00.html" rel="nofollow">http://books.guardian.co.uk/news/articles/0,6109,1125534,00.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2006-12-27</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=First+drafts&amp;rft.atitle=%5B%5BGuardian+Unlimited%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Robert+McCrum&amp;rft.au=Robert+McCrum&amp;rft.date=2004-01-18&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.guardian.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F0%2C6109%2C1125534%2C00.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Of_Mice_and_Men"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
